OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThree asylum seekers have been found
OL,8,Fguilty of raping a woman on Brighton
OL,9,Fbeach while filming the incident in a
OL,10,F"cynical, predatory and callous"
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FIranian national Abdulla Ahmadi, 26,
OL,14,Fand Egyptian nationals Ibrahim
OL,15,FAlshafe, 25, and Karin Al-Danasurt,
OL,16,F20, targeted the woman in the early
OL,17,Fhours of 4 October last year.
OL,19,FAhmadi and Alshafe repeatedly raped
OL,20,Fthe woman on the beach while Al-
OL,21,FDanasurt filmed the incident.
OL,26,@rD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
