PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FAlshafe and Ahmadi, were both found
OL,8,Fguilty of two counts of rape by jurors
OL,9,Fon Thursday. (23 April)
OL,11,FAl-Danasurt was also found guilty of
OL,12,Fall four counts of rape as a secondary
OL,13,Fparty by encouraging and filming the
OL,14,Fordeal.
OL,16,FJurors returned their verdicts in the
OL,17,Ffive-week trial after more than 12
OL,18,Fhours of deliberation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
