PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe court heard Ahmadi and Alshafe met
OL,8,Feach other on a small boat from France
OL,9,Fto the UK, while Alshafe and Al-
OL,10,FDanasurt were roommates.
OL,12,FThey were living at a Home Office-
OL,13,Fapproved hotel accommodation for
OL,14,Fasylum seekers near Horsham in West
OL,15,FSussex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
