PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FJurors were told how the woman had
OL,8,Fbecome separated from her friends
OL,9,Fwhile on a girls' night out, and the
OL,10,Fthree defendants approached her when
OL,11,Fshe was "staggering in the street"
OL,12,Falone.
OL,14,FShe left the Horizon nightclub on the
OL,15,Feastern side of Brighton beach before
OL,16,Fheading to Burger King on Kings Road
OL,17,Faround 5:30am.
OL,19,FCCTV which was shown in court showed
OL,20,Fthe woman interacting with the
OL,21,Fdefendants outside Burger King.
OL,26,@sD@IOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FThe group then cross Kings Road
OL,8,Ftogether on to the promenade and then
OL,9,Fon to the beach where the alleged
OL,10,Fincident took place.
OL,12,FProsecutor Hanna Llewellyn-Waters KC
OL,13,Fhad told jurors: "Frankly, to these
OL,14,Fdefendants, the complainant was meat.
OL,16,F"She was repeatedly abused for their
OL,17,Fsexual gratification and entertainment.
OL,19,F"They wanted sex and that could be
OL,20,Fachieved by being with someone who was
OL,21,Fin no state to resist them."
OL,26,@uD@ROUxD@AOU{D@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FShe said the woman told police she
OL,8,Frecalled being spat on, kicked, and
OL,9,Fher throat being grabbed during the
OL,10,Fattack, as well as men laughing.
OL,12,FGiving evidence in the trial, the
OL,13,Fwoman told the court: "It wasn't
OL,14,Fconsensual, it was not consensual,
OL,15,Fthey are evil and they have ruined my
OL,16,Flife."
OL,26,@uD@WOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
