PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FBeing cross-examined from behind a
OL,8,Fscreen in court, she also cried as she
OL,9,Fsaid: "It's the filmer's face I see
OL,10,Fevery time I close my eyes, laughing
OL,11,Fat me."
OL,13,FIn a video police interview played to
OL,14,Fjurors, recorded on October 13 2025,
OL,15,Fthe victim said she regained
OL,16,Fconsciousness lying on the beach and
OL,17,Fthought she was going to be killed.
OL,26,@qD@GOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
