FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FIn the recording, she said: "I closed
OL,8,Fmy eyes because I thought 'oh my God,
OL,9,Fthey're actually going to kill me', I
OL,10,Fcan hear all these voices and I can't
OL,11,Fstop them."
OL,13,FThe court also heard minutes after
OL,14,Fleaving the men, the woman spoke to
OL,15,Fher friends and was described as
OL,16,F"wailing and hysterical saying she has
OL,17,Fbeen raped".
OL,26,@oD@]OUsD@KO]xD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
