PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FDNA samples were taken from all three
OL,8,Fdefendants, and DNA from both Alshafe
OL,9,Fand Ahmadi matched with samples taken
OL,10,Ffrom the complainant's body during a
OL,11,Fforensic medical examination, while Al-
OL,12,FDanasurt's was inconclusive.
OL,14,FThe prosecution suggested that what
OL,15,Freally happened on the night on
OL,16,FOctober 4 was Alshafe had been knocked
OL,17,Fback by several women and was "on the
OL,18,Fprowl" with the co-defendants.
OL,26,@yD@_OUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
