PN,41510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,F"That night, Mr Alshafe, you were
OL,8,Fnothing more than a nasty little
OL,9,Fpredator," Ms Llewellyn-Waters said to
OL,10,Fhim in court.
OL,12,FAfter the attack the men returned to
OL,13,Ftheir hotel by bus and later had a
OL,14,Fbarbecue together in the evening,
OL,15,Faround the same time the woman was
OL,16,Fwaiting to be medically examined.
OL,18,FA video of Al-Danasurt wearing
OL,19,Ffiltered sunglasses in a selfie with a
OL,20,Flit barbecue was also shown in court.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
