PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FAhmadi left the hotel the day after
OL,8,Fthe rape and moved to an address in
OL,9,FCrewe, Cheshire, where he was arrested
OL,10,Fon October 12, the court heard.
OL,12,FThe move had not been approved by the
OL,13,FHome Office and Ahmadi had been marked
OL,14,Fas "absconding, self-departing" from
OL,15,Fthe accommodation.
OL,17,FOn October 13, Alshafe and Al-
OL,18,FDanasurt, both of of Lower Beeding,
OL,19,Fnear Horsham, were arrested by police
OL,20,Fat their hotel.
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
