CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1777025179
OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,FBorder Security and Asylum Minister
OL,8,FAlex Norris said: "My thoughts are
OL,9,Ffirst and foremost with the victim of
OL,10,Fthis appalling crime, and with all
OL,11,Fthose who have been affected by it.
OL,13,F"What she endured is deeply
OL,14,Fdisturbing, and I commend her bravery
OL,15,Fin coming forward and reporting these
OL,16,Fvile individuals.
OL,18,F"I share the public's outrage in their
OL,19,Fhorrendous actions.
OL,26,@pD@SOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
