OL,3,CThree asylum seekers found guilty of
OL,4,Craping woman on beach in 'callous
OL,5,Cattack'
OL,7,F"The perpetrators have now been
OL,8,Frightly convicted, and justice has
OL,9,Fbeen delivered by the courts.
OL,11,F"Once sentencing has taken place, we
OL,12,Fwill move to deport them off British
OL,13,Fsoil."
